<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Formulier niet beschikbaar</title>
  
  <!-- Favicon -->
  <link rel="icon" type="image/webp" href="/img/favicon-growsocial.webp">
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/webp" href="/img/favicon-growsocial.webp">
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/img/favicon-growsocial.webp">
  
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      background: #f9fafb;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 16px;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 42rem;
      width: 100%;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      padding: 32px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .icon-container {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      background: #fef3c7;
      border-radius: 50%;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .icon-container svg {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      color: #d97706;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 30px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111827;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    p {
      color: #4b5563;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .info-box {
      background: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .info-box p {
      color: #374151;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .actions {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 8px 24px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      display: inline-block;
      background: #ea5d0d;
      color: white;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #d14d07;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="icon-container">
      <svg fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Formulier niet beschikbaar</h1>
    <p>
      Er is nog geen aanvraagformulier ingesteld voor <strong><%= industry.name %></strong>.
    </p>
    <div class="info-box">
      <p>
        Neem contact met ons op via een andere manier, of probeer het later opnieuw.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="actions">
      <a href="/" class="btn">Terug naar homepage</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
